HEADWORD: Arbuscle
<hw>Ar"bus*cle</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>arbuscula</ets> small tree, shrub, dim. of <ets>arbor</ets>
tree.]</ety> <def>A dwarf tree, one in size between a shrub and a tree;
a treelike shrub.</def> <rj><au>Bradley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

